---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Home" description="The Quotient Series by Greg Simpson" hero={true}>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-card">
      <div class="hero-tag">Techno-Thriller</div>
      <h1>The Quotient Series</h1>
      <p>
        Welcome to the home of The Quotient Series. This series centers on Kara McClellan, a scientist and a great
        adventurer. She works on leading edge technology in a world where risk takes her on life-or-death missions around
        the globe.
      </p>
      <p>
        This series of books and stories will bring you to amazing real-world locations and involve the most modern
        technologies and current events. You will be entertained and educated with real science! The story will entertain
        you and the science will be accurate. Kara and her team use technology and science to overcome awesome challenges
        that will keep you turning the pages.
      </p>
      <div class="book-actions">
        <a class="button" href="https://www.simpsong00.com/the-quotient-covenant.html">Read The Quotient Covenant</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/books">See all books</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-art" aria-label="The Quotient Series"></div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Available Now</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <article class="card book-card">
        <img src="https://www.simpsong00.com/uploads/1/3/7/0/137005184/tqc-front-hd_orig.jpg" alt="The Quotient Covenant book cover" />
        <div>
          <p class="meta">Book One</p>
          <h3>The Quotient Covenant</h3>
          <p>
            A silicon chip with 50 Qubits, 1.125 quadrillion computations at the same time, and it is lost. The team of
            scientists that produced the chip are in a race against time to retrieve it.
          </p>
          <p>
            Can they find the chip before it falls into the wrong hands? Or will its immense power be used to destroy the
            world?
          </p>
          <div class="book-actions">
            <a class="button" href="https://www.simpsong00.com/the-quotient-covenant.html">Book details</a>
            <a class="button secondary" href="https://www.simpsong00.com/author.html">Meet the author</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="card book-card">
        <img src="https://www.simpsong00.com/uploads/1/3/7/0/137005184/quantum-time-book-front_orig.jpg" alt="Quantum Time book cover" />
        <div>
          <p class="meta">Book Two</p>
          <h3>Quantum Time</h3>
          <p>
            Kara and her team return to stop a new quantum threat. The story follows the continuing adventures of Kara
            McClellan, the lead scientist in the series, as she and her team attempt to save the world once again.
          </p>
          <div class="book-actions">
            <a class="button" href="https://www.simpsong00.com/quantum-time.html">Book details</a>
            <a class="button secondary" href="/locations">Explore locations</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Explore the World of The Quotient Series</h2>
      <p>
        As a technologist, adventurer, and traveler, I have taken the inspiration from real life experiences and combined
        it with the world of science to bring you compelling adventure stories. Dig into the technology, visit the
        locations, and follow along on the author journey.
      </p>
      <div class="book-actions">
        <a class="button" href="/technology">Technology</a>
        <a class="button" href="/locations">Locations</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/author">Author</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
